Clarify documentation for ackShutdown() and waitUntilShutDown() methods of OsTask and put waitUntilShutDown() in OsTaskWnt destructor to avoid destroying task object before thread is active.
Improper usage of ackShutdown() and waitUntilShutDown() functions may lead to hangs.

